{"tid":1525122,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"諗到個終極方法對付黨鐵！！","createTime":"2019-08-31T19:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:52:57.000Z","uid":132326,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b25ea4471c1de678781f75108d1a6484c79e0739","tid":1525122,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:49:21.000Z","msg":"雖然話黨鐵主要收入唔係車資，但係呢個都未嘗唔係一個方法，就係！！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">喺每個站同車廂開幾罐<span style=\"color: purple;\">臭魚</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/07/Serving_Surstr%C3%B6mming.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F0%2F07%2FServing_Surstr%25C3%25B6mming.jpg&h=b6d1d27d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個站臭氣熏天自然冇人搭黨鐵、冇人流啦！！啲站內舖頭都好快執粒！！"},{"pid":"ee4bda004e0ebe2b27acef3a612231319bc2dc8e","tid":1525122,"uid":308270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:54:58.000Z","msg":"team kill埋良心車長同支持我哋嘅市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc2ba07706690922e6542da027a3636267aab4f","tid":1525122,"uid":52230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:01:05.000Z","msg":"拆閘機正確方法：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">八達通、入票口首要</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">閘門次要</span></span><br />\n唔好睇小港豬鐘意比錢嘅決心"},{"pid":"009a782218eed8159547ae83423e5d9f97e6021e","tid":1525122,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ee4bda004e0ebe2b27acef3a612231319bc2dc8e","tid":1525122,"uid":308270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:54:58.000Z","msg":"team kill埋良心車長同支持我哋嘅市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:01:42.000Z","msg":"最重要將市民心中「黨鐵」同「臭魚」聯繫埋一齊，產生聯感，一諗起黨鐵就諗起個隻獨特既臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國航空、法國航空喺2006年已經禁止帶臭魚罐頭上飛機，大家應該知道會有幾大鑊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a0ddc81aea7a914ea1992e0a4254d840e9b258","tid":1525122,"uid":308270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"009a782218eed8159547ae83423e5d9f97e6021e","tid":1525122,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ee4bda004e0ebe2b27acef3a612231319bc2dc8e","tid":1525122,"uid":308270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:54:58.000Z","msg":"team kill埋良心車長同支持我哋嘅市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:01:42.000Z","msg":"最重要將市民心中「黨鐵」同「臭魚」聯繫埋一齊，產生聯感，一諗起黨鐵就諗起個隻獨特既臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國航空、法國航空喺2006年已經禁止帶臭魚罐頭上飛機，大家應該知道會有幾大鑊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:02:57.000Z","msg":"但印象中一罐都唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋邊到有得買咁大量？"},{"pid":"ac1694e3f35dd8b84db544c0b653d4607a385eda","tid":1525122,"uid":193565,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:08:40.000Z","msg":"用花生麩仲平，花墟12蚊有交易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XjTRDW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XjTRDW.jpg&h=a3526ade&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed258e251bdd1d02b374df62ef5820b9673ed86d","tid":1525122,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac1694e3f35dd8b84db544c0b653d4607a385eda","tid":1525122,"uid":193565,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:08:40.000Z","msg":"用花生麩仲平，花墟12蚊有交易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XjTRDW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XjTRDW.jpg&h=a3526ade&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:10:25.000Z","msg":"用嚟拖地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412a934958137a8500904572b08aa51061457a65","tid":1525122,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ee4bda004e0ebe2b27acef3a612231319bc2dc8e","tid":1525122,"uid":308270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:54:58.000Z","msg":"team kill埋良心車長同支持我哋嘅市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:15:11.000Z","msg":"仲諗其他支持黨鐵嘅人利益？"},{"pid":"1e1bd01f305f5189bba150c1b4aa19aff38be78e","tid":1525122,"uid":143699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:35:51.000Z","msg":"大家冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上今晚黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n完整示範片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b51DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=e0512bbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"dc7fbf538f221d8728490589ae7989b3c640ce13","tid":1525122,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee4bda004e0ebe2b27acef3a612231319bc2dc8e","tid":1525122,"uid":308270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:54:58.000Z","msg":"team kill埋良心車長同支持我哋嘅市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:20:57.000Z","msg":"我相信有良心既車長唔會介意"},{"pid":"fcd97d4ed4757cf9ca4a72d29ce699e027650482","tid":1525122,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果有人唔小心掟左條上部冷氣到會點"}]}